"{\"uid\": \"the42.ie-rhasidat-adeleke-warms-up-for-olympics-with-win-at-diamond-league-6435098-Jul2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"IRELAND'S RHASIDAT Adeleke claimed first place in the 400m at the Diamond League meet in Monaco on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhasidat_Adeleke\", \"score\": 0.9999999999347438, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RHASIDAT Adeleke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhasidat_Adeleke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhasidat_Adeleke\"}, {\"begin\": 66, \"end\": 80, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999993153603625, \"rank\": 6.846400442331242e-07, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 89, \"end\": 95, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"score\": 0.9993156540327497, \"rank\": 0.0006343910074351027, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tallaght athlete triumphed with a time of 49.17 in what was her first ever Diamond League as she came in ahead of beating the Lieke Klaver of the Netherlands and USA's Kendall Ellis.\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 187, \"end\": 201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999993153603625, \"rank\": 6.846400442331242e-07, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 258, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9858913167622753, \"rank\": 0.014270726044340033, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9554158730401919, \"rank\": 0.04665775511834404, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kendall_Ellis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kendall Ellis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kendall_Ellis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kendall_Ellis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was also her second-fastest time ever as she continues her preparations for the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a great one,\\\" Adeleke said after the race.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  \\\"I think it was very well executed, I was very controlled and I was really able to take control of the run from the start.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was running a bit scared because I was on the outside of my main competitors.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I just wanted to make sure I executed my plan for where I was in the race and I think I did that.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have wanted a Diamond League win for a really long time and to have one here at this beautiful stadium, I am really grateful.\\\"\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 